NOTICEMemo No. 57.17.0000.301.31.002.23.118 Date : 15-05-2023
Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  
 (Md. Kapayet Ullah)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 23 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 31 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

NOTICEMemo No. 57.17.0000.301.31.002.23.118 Date : 15-05-2023Page 169 of 1170Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  
 (Md. Kapayet Ullah)
Controller of Examinations

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  
 (Md. Kapayet Ullah)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 436 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 672 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  
 (Md. Kapayet Ullah)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 973 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 1028 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.  Page 1081 of 1170                           ( M A S Kawsar Sarker)

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the

the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.

Note: 
1. The result is hereby published subject to the final approval of the Bangladesh Technical Education Board. If any inadvertent error/mistake is detected later on in the result, the
board as per rule holds the authority of correcting / altering / withdrawing the result at any time. Any comments from the Head of Institutes regarding the published result should be
reported in written within 22 May, 2023. No complain will be entertained after the expiry of the stipulated time.
2. The withheld student must have to clear their withheld status within 22 May, 2023, otherwise they will not get admit card for next examination. After clearing the withheld status
the overall result of the candidates will be published and their candidature in the next examination will be decided accordingly.
